HEADWORD: Legitimation
<hw>Le*git`i*ma"tion</hw> <pr>(-m⟦amac⟧"sh⟦ucr⟧n)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. F. <ets>l⟦eacute⟧gitimation</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of making legitimate.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The coining or <qex>legitimation</qex> of money.</q>
